import torch

def check_cuda():
    if torch.cuda.is_available():
        print("CUDA is available! GPU will be used.")
        print(f"GPU Device Name: {torch.cuda.get_device_name(0)}")
    else:
        print("CUDA is not available. Using CPU.")
